00:01.202 --> 00:04.872
- * Oh, I can't get home fast
enough, Santa Claus *

00:04.905 --> 00:06.507
- I thought you weren't
allowed to do electrical work.

00:06.540 --> 00:08.242
- Oh, no, I'm not allowed to
legally call myself

00:08.276 --> 00:11.145
