supposedly superior values.

02:35.656 --> 02:37.491
- You mean like you do to us
with music.

02:37.525 --> 02:39.126
- Nah, that's different.
I have taste. You don't.

02:39.159 --> 02:40.728
- Taste this.

02:40.761 --> 02:42.530
- Arthur, I've never kicked
anyone out of this church,

02:42.563 --> 02:44.164
